VenderInfo.Name: Cypress
VenderInfo.Description: The Solar-Powered BLE Sensor Beacon RDK provides an easy-to-use platform for the development of a solar-powered IoT device with BLE wireless connectivity. It includes the S6AE103A Energy Harvesting Power Management IC (PMIC) device, which is ideal for solar- or light-powered Energy Harvesting Systems (EHS).

ProductInfo.Name: CYALKIT-E02 Solar-Powered BLE Sensor Beacon RDK

Release.Name: CYALKIT-E02 Solar-Powered BLE Sensor Beacon RDK 1.0 Rev.**

Package.Name: CYALKIT-E02 Solar-Powered BLE Sensor Beacon RDK
Package.Description: The package includes example projects created using the PSoC Creator IDE. Hardware schematics and other design files are also included. A quick start and users guide are available to get familiar with the projects and hardware that comes in the kit.

Version.Name: CYALKIT-E02 Solar-Powered BLE Sensor Beacon RDK 1.0 Rev.**
